Shanna Reed https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shanna_Reed 0 Shanna Reed (born Shanna Herron; October 30, 1955) is an American dancer and television and movie actress. She is known for playing Polly Cooper McGillis on Major Dad. One of seven siblings, she is the daughter of Tommy Reed, the jazz saxophonist and leader of the Tommy Reed Orchestra.Additional television credits include roles in Promised Land, Beverly Hills, 90210, Touched by an Angel, Cheers, Magnum, P.I., The Colbys, Simon Simon, Hotel, I Had Three Wives, Knight Rider, T.J. Hooker, Fantasy Island, Texas, and Newhart. Shanna_Reed ( born Shanna_Herron ; October_30_,_1955 ) is an_American_dancer and television_and_movie_actress .
